{
  "stem": "5371.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or when they brought the Czechoslovakian families from Theresienstadt, beautiful people, beautiful kids-- because I used to go in there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had the chance to go into all these camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I knew what the end result is going to be, because I knew they're not going to let them live, especially with families.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I thought maybe they're going to let the young people stay, or the young women, and they are going to put them to work.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it wasn't the case.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They eliminated the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they-- after that, they brought in Hungarian Jews, women, into that camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they tortured them so much, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They kept them naked, outside the camp there, on the other side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also remember an incident about being in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in 1943.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They brought in a town's worth of Greek Jews, and they brought in about 20 Greek Jews-- [COUGHS] --to my place, to my commander there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[COUGHS] To my place of work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[COUGHS] And they were beaten and kicked for one reason, they couldn't understand the language.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't know how to speak.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They don't know how to speak either German, Jewish, or, or, or any language.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's all they knew, is Greek, or, or some of them knew Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, I, like-- [COUGHS] I had a man, which [INAUDIBLE], a Polish man, which was the architect of the, of the construction, with the name of Vladistok Smalsky And he was heading the construction work.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he took a liking to me because of the similar numbers that we had.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The first four numbers of his were similar to mine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I begged him, I said to him, do me a favor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, let me take care of these Greek Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
